{
  "title": "Artefact — Modernes UI-Kit",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "stack",
      "direction": "vertical",
      "align": "center",
      "gap": "4",
      "padding": "3rem 1.5rem",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "badge",
          "text": "HonoX Hono/JSX Komponenten",
          "size": "lg",
          "colorPalette": "blue",
          "variant": "surface"
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "as": "h1",
          "text": "Ein wunderschön gestaltetes, barrierefreies Komponenten-Set.",
          "size": "5xl",
          "style": "text-align:center;max-width:48rem"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "size": "lg",
          "content": "Ein vollständiges, dreischichtiges Designsystem, das für HonoX, PandaCSS und Sveltia CMS gebaut wurde. Schnell, leichtgewichtig und vollständig barrierefrei, abgestimmt auf gewohnte Nutzungsmuster.",
          "style": "text-align:center;max-width:42rem"
        },
        {
          "type": "stack",
          "direction": "horizontal",
          "gap": "4",
          "children": [
            { "type": "button", "text": "Showcase ansehen", "variant": "solid", "colorPalette": "blue", "size": "lg", "onclick": "window.scrollTo({top: document.getElementById('carousel-showcase').offsetTop - 80, behavior: 'smooth'})" },
            { "type": "button", "text": "Komponenten-Hub", "variant": "outline", "size": "lg", "onclick": "window.scrollTo({top: document.getElementById('hub').offsetTop - 80, behavior: 'smooth'})" }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },

    { "type": "heading", "as": "h2", "text": "Tabs-Showcase", "size": "3xl", "style": "text-align:center", "id": "tabs-showcase" },
    { "type": "text", "size": "md", "content": "Vollständig in reinem Hono/JSX neu implementiert, mit gleitendem Indikator, manueller/automatischer Fokus-Aktivierung und vollständiger Tastaturnavigation.", "style": "text-align:center;max-width:42rem;margin:0 auto" },
    {
      "type": "stack",
      "direction": "vertical",
      "padding": "1.5rem",
      "borderRadius": "1rem",
      "boxShadow": "sm",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "tabs",
          "variant": "enclosed",
          "size": "md",
          "items": [
            {
              "value": "features",
              "label": "⚡ Hauptfunktionen",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "grid",
                  "columns": "{\"base\": 1, \"md\": 3}",
                  "gap": "6",
                  "children": [
                    { "type": "card", "title": "Blitzschnell", "description": "Standardmäßiges SSR mit minimalem statischen Footprint. Hydriert nur, wenn Interaktion nötig ist.", "children": [{ "type": "badge", "text": "Zero-JS-Option", "colorPalette": "green", "variant": "subtle" }] },
                    { "type": "card", "title": "Vollständig barrierefrei", "description": "Folgt exakt den WAI-ARIA-Standards. Vollständig per Tastatur mit roving tabIndex und aria-Zuständen navigierbar.", "children": [{ "type": "badge", "text": "A11y-konform", "colorPalette": "blue", "variant": "subtle" }] },
                    { "type": "card", "title": "Beeindruckendes Design", "description": "Übergänge mit gleitendem Indikator und pixelgenaue Layouts, abgestimmt auf moderne Gewohnheiten.", "children": [{ "type": "badge", "text": "Panda CSS", "colorPalette": "purple", "variant": "subtle" }] }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "value": "pricing",
              "label": "💎 Preispläne",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "grid",
                  "columns": "{\"base\": 1, \"md\": 2}",
                  "gap": "6",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "card",
                      "title": "Starter",
                      "description": "Perfekt für Einzelentwickler und Nebenprojekte, die schnell prototypisieren möchten.",
                      "children": [
                        { "type": "stack", "direction": "horizontal", "align": "baseline", "gap": "1", "children": [
                          { "type": "heading", "as": "p", "text": "$0", "size": "3xl" },
                          { "type": "text", "size": "sm", "content": "/Monat" }
                        ]},
                        { "type": "button", "text": "Loslegen", "variant": "outline", "colorPalette": "blue", "size": "sm" }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "card",
                      "title": "Pro",
                      "description": "Umfangreiche Funktionen, unbegrenzte Seiten, Analyse-Integration und dedizierter Prioritäts-Support.",
                      "children": [
                        { "type": "stack", "direction": "horizontal", "align": "baseline", "gap": "1", "children": [
                          { "type": "heading", "as": "p", "text": "$29", "size": "3xl" },
                          { "type": "text", "size": "sm", "content": "/Monat" }
                        ]},
                        { "type": "button", "text": "Auf Pro upgraden", "variant": "solid", "colorPalette": "blue", "size": "sm" }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "value": "tech-stack",
              "label": "🛠️ Tech-Stack",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "card",
                  "title": "Moderner Web-Stack",
                  "description": "Von Grund auf für maximale Produktionsreife und Geschwindigkeit entwickelt.",
                  "children": [
                    { "type": "stack", "direction": "vertical", "gap": "4", "children": [
                      { "type": "stack", "direction": "horizontal", "justify": "between", "align": "center", "children": [
                        { "type": "text", "size": "sm", "content": "HonoX-Meta-Framework", "style": "font-weight:bold" },
                        { "type": "badge", "text": "Schnell & Server-First", "colorPalette": "orange" }
                      ]},
                      { "type": "stack", "direction": "horizontal", "justify": "between", "align": "center", "children": [
                        { "type": "text", "size": "sm", "content": "Panda CSS", "style": "font-weight:bold" },
                        { "type": "badge", "text": "Zero-Runtime CSS-in-JS", "colorPalette": "amber" }
                      ]},
                      { "type": "stack", "direction": "horizontal", "justify": "between", "align": "center", "children": [
                        { "type": "text", "size": "sm", "content": "Bun-Tooling", "style": "font-weight:bold" },
                        { "type": "badge", "text": "Next-Gen-Geschwindigkeit", "colorPalette": "red" }
                      ]}
                    ]}
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },

    { "type": "heading", "as": "h2", "text": "Hervorgehobene Carousel-Implementierung", "size": "3xl", "style": "text-align:center", "id": "carousel-showcase" },
    { "type": "text", "size": "md", "content": "Zeigt unsere robuste Hono/JSX-Implementierung des Ark-UI-Slider-Carousels. Ziehbar, mit Autoplay und vollständig barrierefrei.", "style": "text-align:center;max-width:42rem;margin:0 auto" },
    {
      "type": "grid",
      "columns": "{\"base\": 1, \"md\": 2}",
      "gap": "8",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "card",
          "title": "Interaktives Autoplay-Carousel",
          "description": "Autoplay-Auslöser, benutzerdefinierte Punkte und Pause beim Hover.",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "carousel",
              "colorPalette": "blue",
              "loop": true,
              "pauseOnHover": true,
              "autoplayDelay": 3000,
              "slides": [
                { "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?w=800&q=80", "caption": "Echtzeit-Analyse — Pulse liefert Live-Daten und Dashboards mit Sub-Sekunden-Streaming-Latenz." },
                { "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518186285589-2f7649de83e0?w=800&q=80", "caption": "KI-gestützte Erkennung — intelligente Anomalieerkennung warnt Ihr Team vor Produktionsausfällen." },
                { "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522071820081-009f0129c71c?w=800&q=80", "caption": "Einheitlicher Team-Arbeitsbereich — teilen Sie annotierte Diagramme und erstellen Sie benutzerdefinierte Bereiche." }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "card",
          "title": "Mehrfach-Slide-Loop-Carousel",
          "description": "Zeigt 2 Slides pro Seite in einem responsiven Raster.",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "carousel",
              "colorPalette": "purple",
              "loop": true,
              "slidesPerPage": 2,
              "spacing": "12px",
              "slides": [
                { "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1557683316-973673baf926?w=600&q=80", "caption": "Slide 1" },
                { "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1557682250-33bd709cbe85?w=600&q=80", "caption": "Slide 2" },
                { "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1557683311-eac922347aa1?w=600&q=80", "caption": "Slide 3" },
                { "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1557682224-5b8590cd9ec5?w=600&q=80", "caption": "Slide 4" },
                { "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1557683316-c31a9d3d0f27?w=600&q=80", "caption": "Slide 5" },
                { "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1557682257-2f9c37a3a5f3?w=600&q=80", "caption": "Slide 6" }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },

    { "type": "heading", "as": "h2", "text": "Interaktiver Komponenten-Hub", "size": "3xl", "style": "text-align:center", "id": "hub" },
    { "type": "text", "size": "md", "content": "Erkunden Sie die umfangreichen Funktionen des Artefact-UI-Komponentensystems, nach Verwendungskategorie gruppiert.", "style": "text-align:center;max-width:42rem;margin:0 auto" },

